data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News Jupiter published an article on the X platform about its February operation dynamics, saying that February is a month for Jupiter's strategic governance decisions and community plans, mainly including: 
1. The active staking rewards (ASR) in the fourth quarter of 2024 went online, distributing 50 million JUP and 75 million DBR to active governance participants; 
2. The JUP buyback plan was officially launched; 
3. The total JUP staked volume hit a new high, exceeding 550 million; 
4. The community audit verified the current total supply of 7 billion JUP, with 2.64 billion in circulation. 
The subsequent key tasks include: 
1. Jupnet development continues to move towards the launch of the mainnet; 
2. Migration from Ape Pro to Trenches began in March; 
3. The Good Cats review and distribution process was completed; 
4. Jupiter Mobile is about to launch a major update.
